{
  "stem": "11882.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And especially the lawyers were largely handicapped by a lack of-- the American and the British lawyers-- by a lack of knowledge of German.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the documentation, which was the philosophy, or what do you want to call it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The style of that trial was documentation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They've written their own prosecution, they felt, the-- the defendants.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Their documents were behind them, and we found them, great clusters of documents, convicting them, boasting of their wonderful deeds that were the crimes of our trial.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so these documents had to be poured through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First found by the Army, which scattered all over Europe and sought them out, brought them to Nuremberg, and they were distributed to-- largely to the so-called research analysts that would then take them to the lawyer concerned if they seemed-- or helped the lawyers concerned if they were puzzled over certain aspects of the documentation, you know.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was our work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could call it translating and interpreting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Including the trial interpretation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But those were the really gifted ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It takes a great gift to be a simultaneous interpreter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A great gift.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We found many very intelligent people learned in both languages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You put them behind that glass cage, in that glass cage, you can't interpret.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That they think differently, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
